# Taste engine rules

- Facts from detectors are authoritative — validate rationale against facts
- Verdicts: generic | drift | intentional | uncertain
- Rationale ≤ 3 sentences, critic voice
- Mock/fallback path required for offline demo
- Use `@taste-engineer` subagent (Opus 4.8)
